data.description: Step back in time and embrace the timeless allure of this charming 1950s home.  This vintage gem boasts its original features, waiting for your personal touch or treasure its originality just the way it is!  With homes selling in the same neighborhood up to a million, this could also be a great opportunity to invest! Laurie Ln is close to all of the wonderful amenities East Memphis has to offer and centrally located!
